y: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">2008</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">年度教育部</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">“</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">中国科技论文在线</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">”</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">优秀评审专家</span></p><p style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">苑涛主编编著的《</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">WTO</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">概论》图书获中国大学出版社图书奖第二届优秀教材奖一等奖（</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">2011.12</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">）。</span></p><p style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">苑涛、吕越，</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">“</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">论当今形势下继续支持出口对中国经济发展的重要性</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">”</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">，</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">中国国际贸易学会</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">2010</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">年</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">“</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">中国外经贸发展与改革</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">”</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">联合征文二等奖。</span></p><p style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">苑涛、佟家栋，</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;">“</